<p>Welcome! You have embarked on a quest!</p>
<p>For the last 2 months I have been hosting a <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-10439274/in-shadow" target="_blank">quest thread</a> on the forums. It was getting to be quite a long post so the audience and I have agreed to port it into its own article. All are welcome to participate and there are no wrong answers&#8230; except the ones that get you killed.</p>
