<p>Hoo-boy. Alright, let's get started.</p>
<ol>
<li>On the phone, let's search Moneybags' Email</li>
<li>On the computer, look at the file inside of the Dumpster</li>
<li>Search the Lodestar Work Orders program.</li>
<li>Finally, go to the AIC Helpdesk and see if there is some way that we could report that our keycard is missing, and see if we could make a new one for us. Perhaps the Employee Database file will help, or something in the sheaf of papers mentioned before? The Badger program would probably help to make the keycard, however.</li>
</ol>
<p>So many things to do&#8230;</p>
<p>Also, my dear friend in the SCPD Discord, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rurascarlet" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5287847); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5287847&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1555903595" alt="RuraScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5287847)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rurascarlet" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5287847); return false;">RuraScarlet</a></span> made some art of Umber &amp; Ben, which can be seen below in the collapsible!</p>
